      <title>美國正在審查中國使用RISC-V晶片技術的風險</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-is-reviewing-risks-chinas-use-risc-v-chip-technology-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根據緻美國立法者的一封信，美國商務部正在審查中國在開源 RISC-V 晶片技術方面的工作對國家安全的影響。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-is-reviewing-risks-chinas-use-risc-v-chip-technology-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 22:13:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美國參議院通過法案迫使 TikTok 撤資，否則將面臨禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/senators-hope-tiktok-will-remain-business-us-under-new-owner-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美國參議院週二晚間以大幅優勢投票，向總統喬·拜登提交立法，要求中國所有者字節跳動在大約九個月內剝離 TikTok 在美國的業務，否則將面臨禁令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/senators-hope-tiktok-will-remain-business-us-under-new-owner-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 21:22:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>希捷預計第四季利潤將因雲端客戶的成長而增加</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/seagate-forecasts-higher-q4-profit-boost-cloud-customers-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由於雲端客戶對其記憶體晶片的需求增加，希捷科技公司週二預測第四季獲利將高於華爾街預期，最近一個季度的獲利預期超出預期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/seagate-forecasts-higher-q4-profit-boost-cloud-customers-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 20:46:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>隨著類比晶片需求的改善，TI 預測第二季營收將高於預期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/analog-chipmaker-texas-instruments-forecasts-quarterly-revenue-above-estimates-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德州儀器 (TI) 週二預測第二季營收高於分析師預期，顯示其模擬半導體需求在長期低迷後有所回升，導致該晶片製造商的股價在盤後交易中上漲 6%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/analog-chipmaker-texas-instruments-forecasts-quarterly-revenue-above-estimates-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 20:13:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
